{
  "id": "adv_main_01_10_07",
  "title": "星見編2章41話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_rival-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "私は、あの子をデビューからずっと見てきた\n――誰よりも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I watched her ever since her debut.\nMore than anyone else.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "だからはっきり言える\nまだ素人同然だった頃の麻奈にすら、貴方は及ばない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I can say this with certainty:\nYou don’t hold a candle to Mana‚ even when she was still an amateur.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.566666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "だから、目の敵にしていたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that why you saw her as your enemy?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.500000000000002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.826258420944217,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "初めてあなたに会った時から思っていました\nお姉ちゃんに対して特別な感情を持ってるって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve had a feeling about you ever since we first met.\nI suspected you had special feelings for my sister.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.15959175427755,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "私は……そんな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-but I… don’t…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.01703655235167,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "分かります\n私もそうですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know you do.\nBecause I do‚ too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "……勘違いしないで。あの子のことは\n同時期にデビューしたアイドルの一人として……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t be mistaken. I only took an interest in Mana\nbecause we were both idols who debuted at the same time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.050369885685015,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "だったら、三枝さんにこだわるのはどうしてですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If that’s true‚ then why are you so interested in Mr. Saegusa?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.68370321901835,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_02-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "………………っ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.383703219018365,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "本気で三枝さんにマネジメントしてほしいわけじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It wasn’t because you wanted Mr. Saegusa to be your manager.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.8170365523517,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "自分じゃなく、お姉ちゃんに才能を見い出した\n三枝さんが許せないからですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was because he discovered the talent in my sister‚ not you‚\nand you resented him for that. Right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.848056875787144,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_02-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さんをバンプロに呼び戻すことで\nお姉ちゃんに勝ったって思いたいだけですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you can get Mr. Saegusa to rejoin Van Productions‚\nyou’ll consider that a victory over my sister‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.17021284370574,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_02-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "…………なっ……何をバカなことを言ってるの？\n私はただ、貴方の現状を……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What?! How can you say something so ridiculous?\nI’m just telling you the state of your circumstances…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.03323985108685,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_02-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "驚きましたか？\n心の中を当てられて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did I scare you?\nBy seeing right into your heart?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.06187068888497,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_02-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "………………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.7177209245061,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_02-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "言っておきますけど、私は長瀬麻奈の妹です\nあなたには、負けません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let me make one thing clear: I am Mana Nagase’s younger sister.\nI’m not going to lose to you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.78438759117276,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（その言葉が莉央の怒りに火をつけたようだった）\n（莉央は琴乃の頬に向かって、手を振り上げる）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Those words seem to light the flame of anger within Rio.)\n(Rio raises a hand‚ aimed at Kotono’s cheek.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.51639553050119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "二人とも、やめるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Stop it! Both of you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.64972886383453,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 83.51639553050117
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8116.937802832141,
          "startTime": 91.76666666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_02-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "……楽しみにしているわ\n貴方が予選も突破出来ずに、恥をかくのを……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I look forward to seeing it.\nTo seeing you fail to pass the preliminary round and cry in shame.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4466.666666666669,
          "startTime": 92.53333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 91.96666666666668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_02-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "――見ていたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did you see all of that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、たまたま通りかかってな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. I just happened to pass by.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_02-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "……見てるだけなんて\nマネージャー失格ですよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And you just stared and did nothing?\nYou’re a failure as a manager.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（強がってはいたが、やはり怖かったんだな）\n（相手は先輩の、しかもトップを走るアイドルだし……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(She was putting up a strong front‚ but of course‚ she was scared.)\n(That was her senpai and an idol racing towards the top‚ at that.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "悪かった\n……でも、きっと同じだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sorry.\nBut the same thing would have happened.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_02-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "俺がいても、琴乃と同じように言い返していたと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I’d stepped in‚ I probably would have said the same things to her that you did.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_02-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "マネージャーがそれでいいんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you sure that’s appropriate behavior for a manager?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "担当するアイドルを守るのが仕事だからな……それに\n本気で、リズノワと肩を並べられると思っているから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ it’s my job to protect the idols I manage. Besides‚\nI really do believe you are equals with LizNoir.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_02-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがとうございます\nさ、行きましょう。遅くなりますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Thank you.\nCome on‚ let’s go. It’s getting late.",
        "id": ""
      },
